text: Rędziny may refer to the following places in Poland: *Rędziny, Lower Silesian Voivodeship (south-west Poland) *Rędziny, Łódź Voivodeship (central Poland) *Rędziny, Częstochowa County in Silesian Voivodeship (south Poland) *Rędziny, Zawiercie County in Silesian Voivodeship (south Poland)
title: Rędziny
